&lt;p&gt;This is a customer-facing role for someone who takes ownership, communicates effectively, and enjoys solving problems. You don&#39;t need to be an engineer, but you should be comfortable learning new technology, investigating issues, and knowing when to escalate concerns to the appropriate team.&lt;/p&gt;
